name: ur boi in space v2
description: what if you were flying through space, as in a dream. everything was going so perfectly + that ufo was checking you out. you were actually living your dream. you always wanted to go where no one had been, experience truly new things. here you find yourself at the outer limits of the known universe; at the the edge of nothing; or the pinnacle of everything. nobody had ever been this far after all...
